Feature: SIM card activation

  # 这个 feature 描述我们微服务对 SIM 卡激活的行为：
  # - 成功激活的情况
  # - 失败激活的情况

  Scenario: Successful SIM card activation
    When I activate a SIM card with ICCID "1255789453849037777" and email "success@example.com"
    Then the activation record with id 1 should be active

  Scenario: Failed SIM card activation
    When I activate a SIM card with ICCID "8944500102198304826" and email "failure@example.com"
    Then the activation record with id 2 should be inactive
